OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThe tower blocks with      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'ladders for cat burglars' 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Lone parent Leonie Ward was fast asleep
OL,6, in her tower block flat when a         
OL,7, neighbour spotted a person dressed in  
OL,8, dark clothing pushing at her window    
OL,9, from the outside.                      
OL,11,FThe would-be-intruder had climbed up to
OL,12,Fthe outside of her flat using          
OL,13,Fscaffolding which has been left in situ
OL,14,Ffor months on end amid a dispute       
OL,15,Fbetween Thurrock Council and its       
OL,16,Fcontractor, Axis.                      
OL,18,FResidents, including Ms Ward, say they 
OL,19,Fare scared, vulnerable and feel        
OL,20,F"trapped" in the three Seabrook Estate 
OL,21,Ftower block flats in Thurrock.         
